comment:
My husband and I are both Domestic Violence survivors. We both heard them frequently get close to our ear & whisper "No one would believe you" 
My husband believed his ex wife for good reason, Johnny is proof that the man is rarely believed. And my husband isn't a little scrawny man, he professionally cosplays as a Viking Berserker, an Ogre and an Orc. 
But he grew up with a father that beat his mother even when his mother would scoop him up. It was just as traumatic for him that his mother would snatch him up while she was being beaten and use him as a shield when dad was that drunk. After they divorced  remembers hiding in the bushes with his brother while their father hunted them with a loaded 10 gauge. Why? Because she waited until he had the kids to serve him with papers demanding he sell the house he built with his own hands not once but twice after a tornado demolished it when it was 75% completed. 
My ex tried to kill me. When I went to court for emergency custody of our toddler I had 4 full sized photo albums of injuries he had inflicted on me in just a few months time. 
What did both of these abusers have in common? They didn't change until we finally had the child they begged to have. In their sick game they both used children as a weapon & pawn thinking they'd trap us with the child & we couldn't leave. 
Thankfully Johnny never had a child with her but if you want to know who the true Johnny Depp is you only have to see what the mother of his children says about him. She knew him 25 years and was with him for 14. It doesn't matter how well or long you think you know someone, you never truly know them until you have lived with them. Having both been in abusive marriages my husband and I saw the telltale signs that Amber was abusing Johnny, their body language changed drastically.
For Jason to NOT pull out of this movie spoke volumes to us & we lost all respect for him. We'll never watch this movie nor will we ever watch any movie that Amber or Jason are in. The news of what happened to Johnny was everywhere, especially that she threw a bottle and cut his fingertip off... My husband also insured the same injury but they couldn't reattach his.

What message did Jason send to his young fans when he's supposed to be Aquaman & he didn't come to help Captain Jack Sparrow. He stayed friends with the woman that hurt him.
